cw(2.75i) |cw(2.75i) 
lw(2.75i) |lw(2.75i) 
.
ATTRIBUTE TYPEATTRIBUTE VALUE
_
MT-LevelUnsafe
.TE

.SH SEE ALSO
.sp
.LP
\fBputwchar\fR(3C), \fBclrtoeol\fR(3CURSES), \fBcurses\fR(3CURSES), \fBcurs_attr\fR(3CURSES), \fBcurs_inwch\fR(3CURSES), \fBcurs_outopts\fR(3CURSES), \fBrefresh\fR(3CURSES), \fBstandout\fR(3CURSES), \fBwinwch\fR(3CURSES), \fBwrefresh\fR(3CURSES), \fBattributes\fR(5)
.SH NOTES
.sp
.LP
The header file <\fBcurses.h\fR> automatically includes the header files <\fBstdio.h\fR>, <\fBunctrl.h\fR> and <\fBwidec.h\fR>.
.sp
.LP
Note that  \fBaddwch()\fR,\fB mvaddwch()\fR, \fBmvwaddwch()\fR, and  \fBechowchar()\fR may be macros.
.sp
.LP
None of these routines can use the color attribute in \fBchtype\fR.
